var book = {
	"name": "Nehemaïah",
	"numChapters": 13,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ki ktien u Nehemaïah u khun u Hakaliah. Ka la jia te ha u 'nai Khisleb, ha ka snem ka ba-arphew, haba nga la don ha ka ïingsyiem Shushan,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> ba u Hanani, uwei na ki para jong nga, u la wan, ma u bad kiwei pat na Judah; bad nga la kylli ïa ki shaphang ki Jiw kiba la ïohlait, kiba la dang sah na ka jingpynwir, bad shaphang ka Jerusalem.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad ki la ong ha nga, “Kita kiba dang sah na ka jingpynwir hangta ha ka shnat ki don ha ka jingjynjar bad ha ka jinglehrain bakhraw: ïa ka kynroh Jerusalem ruh la pyntwa, bad ïa ki khyrdop jong ka la thang da ka ding.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te haba nga la ïohsngew ïa kine ki ktien, nga la shong khop bad nga la ïam, bad nga la sngewsih bun sngi, bad nga la shah jingit, bad nga la duwai ha khmat U Blei ka bneng,",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> bad nga la ong, “Nga kyrpad ïa me, A Trai, U Blei ka bneng, U Blei u bakhraw bad ba-itieng, uba sumar ïa ka jutang bad ïa ka jingisynei bad kita kiba ieit ïa u bad kiba sumar ïa ki hukum jong u:",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> ai ba ka shkor jong me kan shah mynta, bad ba ki khmat jong me kin peit, ba men sngap ïa ka jingduwai u shakri jong me, ïa kaba nga duwai ha khmat jong me ha kane ka por, mynsngi bad mynmiet, na ka bynta ki khun Israel ki shakri jong me, katba nga phla ïa ki pop ki khun Israel, ïa kiba ngi la leh pop ïa me: shisha, ma nga bad ka ïing u kpa jong nga ngi la leh pop.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ngi la leh sniew eh pyrshah ïa me, bad ngim shym la sumar ïa ki hukum, lymne ïa ki aiñ, lymne ïa ki jingbishar, ïa kiba me la hukum ha u Moses u shakri jong me.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> To kynmaw, nga kyrpad ïa me, ïa kata ka ktien ïa kaba me la hukum ha u Moses u shakri jong me, kaba ong, ‘Lada phi ryngkang, ngan pynsakma ïa phi hapdeng ki kynja bynriew:",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> hynrei, lada phin phai sha nga, bad phin sumar ïa ki hukum jong nga bad leh ïa ki, la kiba la beh noh na phi ki don ha ka bakut ka bneng, pynban, ngan ïalum ïa ki nangta, bad ngan wallam ïa ki ha kata ka jaka kaba nga la jied ban sah ka kyrteng jong nga ha ka.’",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Mynta, kine ki long ki shakri jong me bad u paidlang jong me, ïa kiba me la pynim da ka bor bakhraw jong me, bad da ka kti badonbor jong me.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> A Trai, nga kyrpad ïa me, to pynshah mynta ïa ka shkor jong me ha ka jingduwai u shakri jong me, bad ha ki jingduwai ki shakri jong me, kiba sngewbha ban sheptieng ïa ka kyrteng jong me; bad pynman bha, nga kyrpad ïa me, ïa la u shakri ha kane ka sngi, bad ai ka jingisynei ha u ha khmat une u briew.” Namar nga la long u nongrah khuri ïa u syiem."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ha u 'nai Nisan, ha ka snem ka ba-arphew u syiem Artakserksis, haba ka Waiñ ka la don ha khmat jong u, nga la rah ïa ka Waiñ, bad nga la ai ha u syiem. Hynrei, ngam shym la 'matsngewsih ha khmat jong u mynno mynno.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u syiem u la ong ha nga, “Balei ka khmat jong me ka i 'matsngewsih, haba mem da pang?” Kane kam long ei ei, hynrei, tang ka jingsngewsih ka dohnud. Hangta nga la sheptieng shikatdei eh.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad nga la ong ha u syiem, “To u syiem un im junom: ka khmat jong nga kan ym i 'matsngewsih balei, haba ka nongbah, ka jaka ki jingtep ki kpa jong nga, ka sah khlaw, bad ba la thang duh ïa ki khyrdop jong ka, da ka ding?”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ynda kumta, u syiem u la ong ha nga, “Kaei me kyrpad?” Hangta nga la duwai ha U Blei ka bneng.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad nga la ong ha u syiem, “Lada u syiem u sngewbha, bad lada u shakri jong me u la shem ïa ka jingsngewbha ha khmat jong me, ba men da phah ïa nga sha Judah, ha ka nongbah ki jingtep ki kpa jong nga, ba ngan tei ïa ka.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad u syiem u la ong ha nga, (ka syiem ruh ka da shong hajan jong u,) “Ka jingleit jong me kan slem katno? Bad lano men phai pat?” Kumta, u syiem u la sngewbha ban phah ïa nga; bad nga la buh ïa u.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Nalor kane nga la ong ha u syiem, “Lada u syiem u sngewbha, to pynai ki shithi ïa nga ha ki nongsynshar sha shiliang ka wah, ba kin shah ïa nga ban ïaid lait tad ynda nga poi ha Judah;",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> bad ïa ka shithi ha u Asaph u nongap ka khlaw syiem, ba un ai ha nga ïa ki dieng ban shna khung ïa ki khyrdop ka ïingsyiem kiba dei ïa kata ka ïing bad ïa ka kynroh ka nongbah, bad ïa ka ïing sha kaba ngan rung.” Bad u syiem u la ai ha nga, katba kum ka kti babha U Blei jong nga kaba halor jong nga.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ynda kumta, nga la poi ha ki nongsynshar sha shiliang ka wah, bad nga la ai ha ki, ïa ki shithi u syiem. Bad u syiem u la phah ïa ki rangbah shipai bad ïa ki nongshong kulai ryngkat bad nga.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad haba u Sanballat u nong Horon, bad u Tobiah u shakri, u nong Ammon, ki la ïohsngew ïa kata, ka la pynsngewsih ïa ki shikatdei eh, namar ba la wan u briew ban wad ïa ka jingmanbha ki khun Israel.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Kumta, nga la poi ha Jerusalem, bad nga la don hangta, lai sngi.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad nga la khie mynmiet, ma nga bad khyndiat ki briew lem bad nga; bad ngam shym la pyntip ïano ïano ïa kaei ba U Blei jong nga u la buh ha ka dohnud jong nga ban leh ïa ka Jerusalem: bad ym don u kynja mrad lem bad nga, hynrei, tang uta u mrad uba nga la shong halor jong u.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad nga la mih noh mynmiet na Ka Khyrdop Ka Them, shaphang Ka Pukri Ïakjakor, bad sha Ka Khyrdop Synrum, bad nga la khmih bha ïa ki kynroh Jerusalem, kiba la twa, bad ïa ki khyrdop jong ka, ïa kiba la thang da ka ding.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Hadien kata, nga la nang leit sha Ka Khyrdop Umpohliew bad sha ka pung syiem: hynrei, ym lait jaka ïa u mrad ha uba nga shong ban ïaid.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Hadien kata, nga la leit kiew mynmiet narud ka wah duid, bad nga la khmih bha ïa ka kynroh; bad nga la leit phai noh, bad nga la bsut da Ka Khyrdop Ka Them, bad kumta nga la wan phai pat.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te ki nongsynshar kim shym tip shaei nga la leit, lane kaei nga la leh; lymne ngam pat shym la ïathuh ïa kane ha ki Jiw, lymne ha ki lyngdoh, lymne ha ki bakhraw batri, lymne ha ki nongsynshar, lymne ha kita kiwei kiba trei ïa ka kam.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ynda kumta, nga la ong ha ki, “Phi ïohi ïa ka jingshitom ha kaba ngi long, kumno ba ka Jerusalem ka sah khlaw, bad ba la thang ïa ki khyrdop jong ka da ka ding: ïa, ngin ïatei noh ïa ka kynroh Jerusalem, ba ngin ym long ka jinglehrain shuh.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad nga la ïathuh ha ki shaphang ka kti U Blei jong nga kaba la long ka babha halor jong nga; bad ïa ki ktien u syiem ruh kiba u la kren ha nga. Bad ki la ong, “Ïa, ngin ïaïeng bad ngin tei.” Kumta, ki la pynshaitbor la ki kti ïa kane ka kam ka babha.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Hynrei, haba u Sanballat u nong Horon, bad u Tobiah u shakri, u nong Ammon, bad u Geshem u nong Arab, ki la ïohsngew ïa kata, ki la rkhiebeiñ ïa ngi, bad ki la ibeiñ ïa ngi, ki la ong ruh, “Kaei kane ba phi leh? Phin ïaleh pyrshah ïa u syiem?”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Nga la ïathuh te ha ki, bad nga la ong ha ki, “U Blei ka bneng, ma u, un pynman bha ïa ngi; namar kata, ma ngi ki shakri jong u, ngin ïaïeng bad ngin tei: hynrei, phi, phim don ka bynta, lymne ka hok, lymne ka dak jingkynmaw, ha Jerusalem.”"
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ynda kumta, u Eliashib u rangbah lyngdoh u la ïeng joit ryngkat bad ki para jong u ki lyngdoh, bad ki la ïatei ïa Ka Khyrdop Langbrot; ki la pynkyntang ïa ka, bad ki la pynïeng ïa ki jingkhang jong ka; jin haduh ka ïing phira Hammeah ki la pynkyntang ïa ka, haduh ka ïing phira Hananel.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad hajan jong u, ki rangbah Jerikho ki la tei. Bad hajan jong ki, u Sakkur u khun u Imri u la tei.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad ki khun u Hassenaah ki la tei ïa Ka Khyrdop Dohkha; ki la pynshong ïa ki khung jong ka, bad ki la pynïeng ïa ki jingkhang jong ka, ïa ki nar jingkhang jong ka, bad ïa ki dieng-khang jong ka.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad hajan jong ki, u Meremoth u khun u Uriah, u khun u Hakkos, u la shna. Bad hajan jong ki, u Meshullam u khun u Berekhaïah, u khun u Meshesabel, u la shna. Bad hajan jong ki, u Sadok u khun u Baana, u la shna.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad hajan jong ki, ki Tekoi ki la shna: hynrei, ki bakhraw batri jong ki kim shym la buh ïa la ki ryndang ha ka kam u kynrad jong ki.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad u Joïada u khun u Paseah bad u Meshullam u khun u Besodeïah ki la shna ïa ka khyrdop rim; ki la pynshong ïa ki khung jong ka, bad ki la pynïeng ïa ki jingkhang jong ka, bad ïa ki nar jingkhang jong ka, bad ïa ki dieng-khang jong ka.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad hajan jong ki, u Melatiah u nong Gibeon, bad u Jadon u nong Meronoth, ki rangbah Gibeon, bad Mispah, kiba dei ïa ka khet u nongsynshar sha shiliang ka wah, ki la shna.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Hajan jong u, u la shna u Ussiel u khun u Harhaïah, ki bania. Bad hajan jong u, u Hananiah uwei na ki apothekari, bad ki la shna pynskhem ïa ka Jerusalem haduh ka kynroh rben.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad hajan jong ki, u la shna u Rephaïah u khun u Hur, u nongsynshar jong ka shiteng ka ilaka Jerusalem.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad hajan jong ki, u Jedaïah u khun u Harumaph u la shna, marpyrshah ïa la ka ïing. Bad hajan jong u, u la shna u Hattush u khun u Hashabniah.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> U Malkhijah u khun u Harim, bad u Hasshub u khun u Pahath-moab, ki la shna ïa kawei pat ka bynta, bad ïa ka ïing phira ki pajwa.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad hajan jong u, u la shna u Shallum u khun u Hallohesh, u nongsynshar jong ka shiteng ka ilaka Jerusalem, ma u bad ki khun kynthei jong u.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ïa Ka Khyrdop Ka Them, u la shna u Hanun, bad ki nong Sanoah, ki la tei ïa ka, bad ki la pynïeng ïa ki jingkhang jong ka, ïa ki nar jingkhang jong ka, bad ïa ki dieng-khang jong ka, bad shi hajar pruh na ka kynroh haduh Ka Khyrdop Synrum.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad ïa Ka Khyrdop Synrum, u la shna u Malkhijah u khun u Rekhab, u nongsynshar ka ilaka Beth-hakkerem; u la tei ïa ka, bad u la pynïeng ïa ki jingkhang jong ka, ïa ki nar jingkhang jong ka, bad ïa ki dieng-khang jong ka.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad ïa Ka Khyrdop Umpohliew, u la shna u Shallum u khun u Kol-hoseh, u nongsynshar ka ilaka Mispah, u la tei ïa ka, bad u la sop ïa ka, bad u la pynïeng ïa ki jingkhang jong ka, ïa ki nar jingkhang jong ka, bad ïa ki dieng-khang jong ka, bad ïa ka kynroh ka pung Shiloah hajan ka kper syiem, bad haduh ki kyrdon kiba hiar arsut na ka nongbah u Dabid.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Nadien jong u, u la shna u Nehemaïah u khun u Asbuk, u nongsynshar jong ka shiteng ka ilaka ka Beth-sur, haduh kata ka jaka kaba marpyrshah ïa ki jingtep u Dabid, bad haduh kata ka pung ba la shna, bad haduh ka ïing ki rangbah badonbor.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Nadien jong u, ki la shna ki Lebi, u Rehum u khun u Bani. Hajan jong u, u la shna u Hashabiah, u nongsynshar jong ka shiteng ka ilaka Keilah, ïa la ka ilaka.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Nadien jong u, ki para jong ki, ki la shna, u Babbai u khun u Henadad, u nongsynshar jong ka shiteng ka ilaka Keilah.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad hajan jong u, u la shna u Eser u khun u Jeshua, u nongsynshar ka Mispah, ïa kawei pat ka bynta, kaba marpyrshah ïa kaba kiew sha ka ïing buh atiar ïapom ha ka pyrkhung ka kynroh.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Nadien jong u, u Barukh u khun u Sabbai da kaba sngew-shitrhem u la shna ïa kawei pat ka bynta na ka pyrkhung ka kynroh haduh ka jingkhang ka ïing u Eliashib u rangbah lyngdoh.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Nadien jong u, u Meremoth u khun u Uriah u khun u Hakkos u la shna ïa kawei pat ka bynta, naduh ka jingkhang u Eliashib haduh ka bakut ka ïing u Eliashib.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bad nadien jong u, ki la shna ki lyngdoh; ki rangbah na Ka Pyntha.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Nadien jong ki, u Benjamin bad u Hasshub ki la shna ïa kaba marpyrshah ïa la ka ïing. Nadien jong ki, u Asaraïah u khun u Maaseïah u khun u Ananiah u la shna hajan la ka ïing.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Nadien jong u, u Binnui u khun u Henadad u la shna ïa kawei pat ka bynta, na ka ïing u Asaraïah haduh ka pyrkhung ka kynroh, bad haduh ka dong.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> U Palal u khun u Usai u la shna marpyrshah ïa ka pyrkhung ka kynroh, bad ïa ka ïing phira kaba pynkha na ka ïingsyiem kaba haneng kaba hajan ka phyllaw ka karod. Nadien jong u, u Pedaïah u khun u Parosh.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> (Bad ki Nethin ki la shong sah ha Ophel, haduh kata ka jaka kaba marpyrshah Ka Khyrdop Um shaphang mihngi, bad ïa ka ïing phira kaba pynkha.)",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Nadien jong u, ki Tekoi ki la shna ïa kawei pat ka bynta, kaba marpyrshah ka ïing phira bakhraw kaba pynkha, bad haduh ka kynroh Ophel.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Haneng Ka Khyrdop Kulai, ki lyngdoh ki la shna, uwei pa uwei marpyrshah ïa la ka ïing.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Nadien jong ki, u Sadok u khun u Immer u la shna marpyrshah ïa la ka ïing. Bad nadien jong u, u la shna u Shemaïah u khun u Shekhaniah, u nongap Ka Khyrdop Mihngi.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Bad nadien jong u, ki la shna u Hananiah u khun u Shelemiah, bad u Hanun u khun bahynriew u jong u Salaph, ïa kawei pat ka bynta. Nadien jong u, u Meshullam u khun u Berekhaïah u la shna marpyrshah ïa la ka kamra.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Nadien jong u, u la shna u Malkhijah uwei na ki bania haduh ka ïing ki Nethin, bad ki jong ki nongkhaïi, marpyrshah ïa Ka Khyrdop Hammiphkad bad haduh kaba kiew ka dong.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Bad hapdeng kaba kiew ka dong bad Ka Khyrdop Langbrot, ki bania bad ki nongkhaïi ki la shna."
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Hynrei, haba u Sanballat u la ïohsngew ba ngi la ïatei ïa ka kynroh, u la sngewbitar, bad u la ing khait, bad u la krenbeiñ ïa ki Jiw.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u la kren ha khmat la ki para bad ïa ka kynhun shipai Samaria, bad u la ong, “Kine ki Jiw ba khlem bor ki leh aïu? Kin ker kut ïa lade? Kin kñia? Kin pyndep ha kawei ka sngi? Kin khyllie pat ïa ki maw na kine ki lymbher tait, haba ki la ing ruh?”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad u Tobiah u nong Ammon u la don hajan jong u, bad u la ong, “Wat ïa kata kaba ki tei, lada u ksar un kiew, un pyntwa noh ïa ka kynroh maw jong ki.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> “To sngew, A U Blei jong ngi, namar la ibeiñ ïa ngi; pynphai pat ïa ka jingkrenbeiñ jong ki halor ka khlieh jong ki hi, bad aiti noh ïa ki kum ka jinglute ha ka ri ka jingpynwir:",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> bad wat tap noh ïa ki jingleh bymhok jong ki, bad wat ai ba yn pyndam noh ïa ki pop jong ki na khmat jong me: namar ki la pynkhih bitar ïa me ha khmat ki nongtei.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Kumta, ngi la tei ïa ka kynroh; bad ïa ka kynroh baroh kawei la pynïadait lang haduh marshiteng ka jingjrong jong ka: namar u paidlang u la ai la ka jingmut ban trei.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Hynrei, haba u Sanballat, bad u Tobiah, bad ki Arab, bad ki Ammon, bad ki Ashdod, ki la ïohsngew ba la nang shna nang shna ïa ki kynroh Jerusalem, bad ba la sdang ban pyndap ïa ki jingtwa, te ki la sngewshla eh:",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> bad baroh ki la ïasylla lang ban wan ïaleh ïa ka Jerusalem, bad ban pynkulmar ïa ka.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Hynrei, ngi la ïaduwai ha U Blei jong ngi, bad ngi la buh nongap ban ïaleh ïa ki mynsngi bad mynmiet, namar jong ki.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad ki Judah ki la ong, “Ka bor ki nongkit jingkit ka la duh, bad dang don shibun ki synrum; kumta ngi ngim lah ban tei ïa ka kynroh.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad ki nongïaleh pyrshah jong ngi ki la ong, “Kin ym ïoh tip, lymne kin ym ïohi, tad ynda ngi la poi hapdeng jong ki, bad ngi la pynïap ïa ki, bad ngi la pynpep ïa ka kam.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te haba ki Jiw kiba shong marjan ïa ki, ki la poi, ki la ong ha ngi shiphew sien na ki jaka baroh, “Ka dei ba phin phai pat sha ngi.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Namar kata, nga la buh ha ki bynta kiba kham tbian ka jaka kaba shadien ka kynroh, ha ki jaka kiba lait, nga la buh ïa u paidlang katba kum ki ïing jong ki bad la ki waitlam, bad la ki sum, bad la ki ryntieh.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad nga la khmih, bad nga la ïeng joit, bad nga la ong ha ki bakhraw batri, bad ha ki nongsynshar, bad ha kita kiwei pat na u paidlang, “Wat sheptieng ïa ki: kynmaw ïa U Trai, uba long u bakhraw bad ba-itieng, ban ïaleh na ka bynta la ki para, la ki khun shynrang bad la ki khun kynthei, la ki tnga bad la ki ïing.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad haba ki nongshun jong ngi ki la ïohsngew ba ngi la tip ïa kane, bad ba U Blei u la pyndam noh ïa ka jingsylla jong ki, ngi baroh ngi la leit pat sha ka kynroh, uwei pa uwei ha la ka kam.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad naduh kata ka por, marshiteng ki shakri jong nga ki la trei ha kata ka kam, bad marshiteng ki la bat ïa ki sum, ïa ki stieh, bad ïa ki ryntieh, bad ïa ki jingphong nar; bad ki nongsynshar ki la don shadien ka ïing Judah baroh.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Kita kiba tei ïa ka kynroh bad kita kiba kit jingkit ki la pynkit ïa lade, uwei pa uwei da kawei ka kti u la trei ïa ka kam, bad da kawei u la bat la ka atiar;",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> bad ki nongtei ruh, uwei pa uwei u la kieng ïa la ka waitlam ha la ka krung, bad kumta ki la tei. Bad uta uba put ronsing u la don hajan jong nga.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad nga la ong ha ki bakhraw batri, bad ha ki nongsynshar, bad ha kita kiwei pat na u paidlang, “Ka kam ka long ka bakhraw bad kaba bun, bad ngi la saphred halor ka kynroh, jngai uwei na uwei pat:",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> ha kano kano ka jaka phi ïohsngew ïa ka ronsing, ïalang hangta ha ngi; U Blei jong ngi un ïaleh na ka bynta jong ngi.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Kumta, ngi la trei ïa ka kam: bad marshiteng ki la bat ïa ki sum naduh kaba shai byrngut haduh kaba mih ki khlur.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Nga la ïathuh ruh ha kajuh ka por ha u paidlang, “To uwei pa uwei lem bad la u shakri un thiah miet ha Jerusalem, ba kin ap phira ïa ngi mynmiet, bad ba kin trei mynsngi.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Kumta, lymne ma nga, lymne ki para jong nga, lymne ki shakri jong nga, lymne ki nongap kiba bud ïa nga, ngim shym la loit noh ïa la ki jaiñ, uwei pa uwei bad la ka atiar u leit sha um."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te la mih jinglynñiar bakhraw u paidbah bad ki tnga jong ki pyrshah ïa la ki para ki Jiw.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Namar don kiba la ong, “Ma ngi, ki khun shynrang jong ngi bad ki khun kynthei jong ngi, ngi long bun; to ai Kew ïa ngi, ba ngin bam bad ba ngin im.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Don kiwei pat kiba ong, “Ngi la buh bynda ïa la ki lyngkha, bad ïa la ki brisoh Waiñ, bad ïa la ki ïing: to ai Kew ïa ngi, namar ka 'nemsniew.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Don ruh kiba ong, “Ngi la shim kylliang tyngka ïa ka khajna u syiem halor ki lyngkha jong ngi bad ki brisoh Waiñ jong ngi.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Hynrei te ka doh jong ngi ka long kum ka doh ki para jong ngi, ki khun jong ngi kum ki khun jong ki; bad ha khmih, ngi buh mraw ïa la ki khun shynrang bad ïa la ki khun kynthei, ban long ki shakri, bad don lypa kiba na ki khun kynthei jong ngi ïa kiba la ring mraw: bad kam long ha ka bor jong ngi ban khang ïa kata; namar kiwei pat ki briew ki la ïoh noh ïa ki lyngkha bad ïa ki brisoh Waiñ jong ngi.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te nga la bitar shikatdei eh haba nga la ïohsngew ïa ka jinglynñiar jong ki bad ïa kine ki ktien.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Nga la pyrkhat te ha lade, bad nga la byrngem ïa ki bakhraw batri bad ïa ki nongsynshar, bad nga la ong ha ki, “Phi shim sut, uwei pa uwei na la u para.” Bad nga la pynlong ka jingïaseng bah ban ïaleh ïa ki.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad nga la ong ha ki, “Ma ngi katba shong ka bor jong ngi, ngi la thied ïa la ki para ki Jiw, ïa kiba la die noh ha ki Jentil; phi, pynban, phi die ïa la ki para, bad ka dei du ban die noh ïa ki ha ngi?” Te ki la sngap jar, bad kim shym la shem kawei ka jubab.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Nga la ong ruh, “Kane kaba phi leh kam long ka babha: hato kam dei ïa phi ban ïaid ha ka jingsheptieng ïa U Blei jong ngi, namar ka jingrkhiebeiñ ki Jentil ki nongshun jong ngi?",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ma nga ruh, ki para jong nga bad ki shakri jong nga, ngi ai sut ïa ki, da ki tyngka bad da u Kew. Nga kyrpad ïa phi, to ngin iehnoh noh ïa kane ka sut.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Nga kyrpad ïa phi, to ai noh pat ha ki, mynta ka sngi, ïa ki lyngkha jong ki, ïa ki brisoh Waiñ jong ki, ïa ki bri Olib jong ki, bad ïa ki ïing jong ki, bad shi bynta na ka shispah na ki tyngka, bad na u Kew, na ka Waiñ bad ka umphniang, kiba phi khrong bor na ki.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ynda kumta, ki la ong, “Ngi ngin ai pat ïa ki, bad ngin ym pan ei ei na ki, kumta ngin leh, kumba me ong.” Ynda kumta, nga la khot ïa ki lyngdoh, bad nga la pynsmai ïa ki, ba kin leh katba kum kane ka jingkular.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Nga la kynther noh ruh ïa ka rmiang ka jaiñ jong nga, bad nga la ong, “Kumta U Blei un kynther noh ïa u briew baroh na ka ïing jong u, bad na ka kam jong u, u ban ym pyndep ïa kane ka jingkular; kumne keiñ, yn kynther noh ïa u, bad ba yn pynsuda ïa u.” Bad u paidbah baroh u la ong, “Amen,” bad ki la ïaroh ïa U Trai. Bad u paidbah u la leh katba kum kane ka jingkular.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Nalor kane ruh, naduh kata ka por ba la thung ïa nga u nongsynshar jong ki ha ka ri Judah, naduh ka snem ka ba-arphew haduh ka snem ka balaiphew ar u Artakserksis u syiem, kata ka long, khat-ar snem, ma nga bad ki para jong nga ngim shym la bam u kpu nongsynshar.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Hynrei, ki nongsynshar kiba mynshuwa jong nga ki la ban khia ïa u paidbah, bad ki la shim ïa u kpu bad ka Waiñ na ki, nalor ki sawphew shekel rupa; shisha keiñ, wat ki shakri jong ki, ki la leh trai khlieh halor u paidbah: hynrei, nga ngam shym la leh kumta, namar kaba tieng ïa U Blei.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Shisha, nga la neh ruh ha ka jingtrei kane ka kynroh, bad ngim shym la thied khyndew ei ei ruh: bad ki shakri jong nga baroh ki la ïalang hangta ha kata ka kam.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Nalor kane ruh, la don ha ka miej jong nga na ki Jiw bad na ki nongsynshar shispah sanphew ngut ki briew, nalor kita kiba la wan sha ngi napdeng ki Jentil kiba baroh sawdong ïa ngi.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad kata kaba la khreh man la ka sngi, ka la long uwei u masi dab bad hynriew tylli ki langbrot ba la kynsai; bad ki sim ruh kiba la khreh ïa nga, bad man ka shiphew sngi ki kynja Waiñ baroh kyrhai: la kumta ruh, ngam shym la pan ïa u kpu nongsynshar, namar ba ka jingban ka la long kaba khia halor une u paidbah.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> “Kynmaw ïa nga, A U Blei jong nga ban pynbha, ïa kaba nga la leh baroh ïa une u paidbah.”"
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad haba la pynbna ha u Sanballat bad u Tobiah, bad ha u Geshem u nong Arab, bad ha kita kiwei pat na ki nongshun jong ngi, ba nga la lah tei ïa ka kynroh, bad ba ym shym la iehnoh ïa kaba lait ha ka; (la haduh kata ka por ngam pat shym la pynïeng ïa ki jingkhang ha ki khyrdop;)",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> u Sanballat bad u Geshem ki la phah ha nga, ki ïa-ong, “Ale, to ngin ïashem ha kawei na ki nongrit ha ka pyntha Ono.” Hynrei, ki la thmu ban pynmynsaw ïa nga.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad nga la phah ïa ki nonglam-ktien ha ki, nga da ong, “Nga dang trei ïa ka kam kaba khraw, namar kata ngam lah ban wan hiar: balei kan pep ka kam, katba nga iehnoh ïa ka, bad ngan wan sha phi?”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad ki la phah kumne sha nga saw sien; bad nga la phai ktien ïa ki kumjuh hi.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ynda kumta, u Sanballat u la phah ïa la u shakri sha nga kumjuh hi ka basan sien bad ka shithi khlem bon ha ka kti jong u;",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> ha kaba la thoh, “La bna hapdeng ki jaid bynriew, bad u Gashmu u ong ïa kata, ba ma me bad ki Jiw phi thmu ban ïaleh pyrshah; ba namar kata me tei ïa ka kynroh: bad ba me kwah ban long u syiem jong ki, katba kum kine ki ktien.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad ba me thung ïa ki nongïathuhlypa ban ïathuhkhana shaphang jong me ha Jerusalem, ki ïa-ong, ‘Don u syiem ha Judah’: bad mynta yn pynbna ha u syiem katba kum kine ki ktien. Ale te namar kata, ngin ïapyrkhat lang.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ynda kumta, nga la phah ha u, nga da ong, “Ym shym la leh ei ei ruh kum kita kiba me ong, hynrei, me shu thaw ïa ki na ka dohnud jong me hi.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Namar, ki baroh, ki la kwah ban pynsheptieng ïa ngi, ki ïa-ong, “Yn pyntlot bor ïa ki kti jong ki na kata ka kam, ba yn ym pyndep ïa ka.” “Hynrei, mynta, A U Blei, pynshaitbor ma me ïa ki kti jong nga.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad nga la leit ha ka ïing u Shemaïah u khun u Delaïah u khun u Mehetabel, uba la khang khop ïa lade; bad u la ong, “To ngin ïashem ha ka ïing U Blei, hapoh ka templ, bad ngin khang ïa ka jingkhang ka templ: namar kin wan ban pynïap ïa me; shisha keiñ, ha kaba mynmiet kin wan ban pynïap ïa me.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad nga la ong, “Hato dei u briew uba kat nga u ban phet ïap noh? bad don mano uba kat nga, u ban leit ha ka templ ïa ka ban ri pynim ïa lade? Ngan ym leit bsut.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad nga la sngewthuh, bad, ha khmih, U Blei um shym la phah ïa u: hynrei, u la kren ïa kane ka jingïathuhlypa pyrshah ïa nga: bad u Tobiah bad u Sanballat ki la wer nong ïa u.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na ka bynta kane keiñ, ki la wer ïa u, ba ngan dup sheptieng, bad ba ngan leh kumta, bad ba ngan leh pop, ba kin ïoh daw ban pynbna nam basniew, ba ki lah ban rkhiebeiñ ïa nga.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> “Kynmaw, A U Blei jong nga, ïa u Tobiah bad ïa u Sanballat katba kum kine ki kam jong ki, bad ïa ka Noadiah ka nongïathuhlypa, bad ïa kita kiwei pat ki nongïathuhlypa kiba la kwah ban pynsheptieng ïa nga.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Kumta, la pyndep ïa ka kynroh ha ka ba-arphew san sngi u 'nai Elul, ha ki sanphew ar sngi.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad haba ki nongshun jong ngi baroh, ki la ïohsngew ïa kata, ki Jentil baroh kiba sawdong ïa ngi, ki la tieng, bad ki la sngewjew liaw eh ha lade: namar ki la sngewthuh ba la leh ïa kane ka kam da U Blei jong ngi.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Nalor kane ruh, ha kita ki sngi, ki bakhraw batri ki Judah ki la phah bun ki shithi ha u Tobiah, bad ki shithi u Tobiah ki la poi sha ki.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Namar don bun ha Judah kiba ha ka jingïasylla bad u, namar u la long u pyrsa kurim u Shekaniah u khun u Arah; bad u khun jong u, u Jehohanan u la shongkurim ïa ka khun u Meshullam u khun u Berekhaïah.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ki la kren ruh de shaphang ki jingleh babha jong u ha khmat jong nga, bad ki la ïathuh ïa ki ktien jong nga ha u. Bad u Tobiah u la phah shithi ban pynsheptieng ïa nga."
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad haba la lah tei ïa ka kynroh, bad ba nga la lah pynïeng ïa ki jingkhang, bad ba la thung ïa ki nongap jingkhang bad ïa ki nongrwai bad ïa ki Lebi,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> nga la ai hukum ïa u Hanani u para jong nga, bad ïa u Hananiah u nongsynshar ka ïing phira, shaphang ka Jerusalem: namar u long u briew uba ïaineh, bad uba kham sheptieng ïa U Blei ban ïa kiba bun.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad nga la ong ha ki, “Wat ai ba yn plie ïa ki khyrdop ka Jerusalem tad ynda ka la shit ka sngi: bad katba kin ïeng ban ap, to kin khyrdep ïa ki jingkhang, bad khang ma phi: bad buh ki jingap kylliang na ki trai-shnong Jerusalem, uwei pa uwei ha la ka jingap jingap, bad uwei pa uwei marpyrshah ïa la ka ïing.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad kane ka nongbah ka la long kaba ïar bad kaba khraw: hynrei, ki briew ha ka ki la long kiba khyndiat, bad ym shym la tei ïa ki ïing.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad U Blei jong nga u la buh ha ka dohnud jong nga ban ïalum lang ïa ki bakhraw batri, bad ïa ki nongsynshar, bad ïa u paidbah, ba yn kheiñ ïa ki katba kum ka jingkha pateng jong ki. Bad nga la shem ïa ka kitab ka jingkha pateng jong kita kiba la wan kiew ha kaba nyngkong, bad nga la shem ba la thoh ha ka.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Kine ki long ki khun kata ka shnat, kiba la leit kiew na ka jingpynwir jong kita ïa kiba la ring noh, kiba u Nebukhadnessar u syiem ka Babilon u la ring noh, bad kiba la wan phai pat ha Jerusalem bad ha Judah, uwei pa uwei ha la ka shnong;",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> kiba la wan ryngkat bad u Serubbabel, u Jeshua, u Nehemaïah, u Asaraïah, u Ramiah, u Nahamani, u Mordekai, u Bilshan, u Mispereth, u Bigbai, u Nehum, u Baanah. Ka jingkheiñ ki rangbah u paidbah Israel:",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> ki khun u Parosh, ar hajar shispah hynñiewphew ar.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ki khun u Shephatiah, laispah hynñiewphew ar.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ki khun u Arah, hynriewspah sanphew ar.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ki khun u Pahath-moab, na ki khun u Jeshua bad u Joab, ar hajar phraspah khatphra.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ki khun u Elam, shi hajar arspah sanphew saw.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ki khun u Sattu, phraspah sawphew san.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ki khun u Sakkai, hynñiewspah hynriewphew.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ki khun u Binnui, hynriewspah sawphew phra.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ki khun u Bebai, hynriewspah arphew phra.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ki khun u Asgad, ar hajar laispah arphew ar.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ki khun u Adonikam, hynriewspah hynriewphew hynñiew.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ki khun u Bigbai, ar hajar hynriewphew hynñiew.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ki khun u Adin, hynriewspah sanphew san.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ki khun u Ater, na u Hesekaïah, khyndaiphew phra.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ki khun u Hashum, laispah arphew phra.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ki khun u Besai, laispah arphew saw.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ki khun u Hariph, shispah khat-ar.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Ki khun u Gibeon, khyndaiphew san.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Ki rangbah Bethlehem bad Netophah, shispah phraphew phra.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ki rangbah Anathoth, shispah arphew phra.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Ki rangbah Beth-asmabeth, sawphew ar.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Ki rangbah Kiriath-jearim, Khephirah, bad Beeroth, hynñiewspah sawphew lai.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Ki rangbah Ramah bad Gaba, hynriewspah arphew wei.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Ki rangbah Mikhmash, shispah arphew ar.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Ki rangbah Bethel bad Ai, shispah arphew lai.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Ki rangbah kawei pat ka Nebo, sanphew ar.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Ki khun uwei pat u Elam, shi hajar arspah sanphew saw.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Ki khun u Harim, laispah arphew.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Ki khun u Jerikho, laispah sawphew san.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Ki khun u Lod, u Hadid, bad u Ono, hynñiewspah arphew wei.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Ki khun u Senaah, lai hajar khyndaispah laiphew.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Ki lyngdoh: ki khun u Jedaïah na ka ïing u Jeshua, khyndaispah hynñiewphew lai.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Ki khun u Immer, shi hajar sanphew ar.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Ki khun u Pashur, shi hajar arspah sawphew hynñiew.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Ki khun u Harim, shi hajar khathynñiew.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Ki Lebi: ki khun u Jeshua, u Kadmiel, bad na ki khun u Hodebah, hynñiewphew saw.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Ki nongrwai: ki khun u Asaph, shispah sawphew phra.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Ki nongap jingkhang: ki khun u Shallum, ki khun u Ater, ki khun u Talmon, ki khun u Akkub, ki khun u Halita, ki khun u Shobai, shispah laiphew phra.",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Ki Nethin: ki khun u Siha, ki khun u Hasupha, ki khun u Tabbaoth;",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> ki khun u Keros, ki khun u Sia, ki khun u Padon;",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> ki khun u Lebanah, ki khun u Hagaba, ki khun u Shalmai;",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> ki khun u Hanan, ki khun u Giddel, ki khun u Gahar;",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> ki khun u Reaïah, ki khun u Resin, ki khun u Nekoda;",
			"51": "<sup>51</sup> ki khun u Gassam, ki khun u Ussa, ki khun u Phaseah;",
			"52": "<sup>52</sup> ki khun u Besai, ki khun u Meunim, ki khun u Nephushesim;",
			"53": "<sup>53</sup> ki khun u Bakbuk, ki khun u Hakupha, ki khun u Harhur;",
			"54": "<sup>54</sup> ki khun u Basleth, ki khun u Mehida, ki khun u Harsha;",
			"55": "<sup>55</sup> ki khun u Barkhos, ki khun u Sisera, ki khun u Temah;",
			"56": "<sup>56</sup> ki khun u Nesiah, ki khun u Hatipha.",
			"57": "<sup>57</sup> Ki khun ki shakri u Solomon: ki khun u Sotai, ki khun u Sophereth, ki khun u Perida;",
			"58": "<sup>58</sup> ki khun u Jaala, ki khun u Darkon, ki khun u Giddel;",
			"59": "<sup>59</sup> ki khun u Shephatiah, ki khun u Hattil, ki khun u Pokhereth-hassebaim, ki khun u Amon.",
			"60": "<sup>60</sup> Ki Nethin baroh, bad ki khun ki shakri u Solomon, ki la long laispah khyndaiphew ar.",
			"61": "<sup>61</sup> Bad kine ki la long kita kiba leit kiew na Tel-melah, u Tel-haresha, u Kherub, u Addon, bad u Immer: hynrei, kim lah ban pyni ïa ki ïing ki kpa jong ki, lymne ïa ka jingkha pateng jong ki, la ki la long ne em na Israel:",
			"62": "<sup>62</sup> ki khun u Delaïah, ki khun u Tobiah, ki khun u Nekoda, hynriewspah sawphew ar.",
			"63": "<sup>63</sup> Bad na ki lyngdoh: ki khun u Hobaïah, ki khun u Hakkos, ki khun u Barsillai, uba la shongkurim ïa kawei na ki khun kynthei u Barsillai u nong Gilead, bad la khot ïa u da ka kyrteng jong ki.",
			"64": "<sup>64</sup> Kine ki la ïawad ïa la ka rejistor hapdeng kita kiba la kheiñ katba kum ka jingkha pateng jong ki, hynrei, ym shym la shem ïa ka: namar kata, la ñiew sang ïa ki, bad la kyntait ïa ki na ka kam lyngdoh.",
			"65": "<sup>65</sup> Bad u Tirshatha u la ong ha ki, ba kin ym ïoh bam na kiei kiei ki bakyntang tam, tad ynda un ïeng u lyngdoh uba don Urim bad Thummim.",
			"66": "<sup>66</sup> U paidbah baroh lang u la long sawphew ar hajar laispah hynriewphew,",
			"67": "<sup>67</sup> nalor ki shakri shynrang bad ki shakri kynthei jong ki, na kiba la don hynñiew hajar laispah laiphew hynñiew: bad ki la don arspah sawphew san ki nongrwai shynrang bad ki nongrwai kynthei.",
			"68": "<sup>68</sup> Ki kulai jong ki, ki la long hynñiewspah laiphew hynriew; ki khashor jong ki, arspah sawphew san;",
			"69": "<sup>69</sup> ki ut, sawspah laiphew san: ki kadda, hynriew hajar hynñiewspah arphew.",
			"70": "<sup>70</sup> Bad don kiba napdeng ki rangbah ki ïing ki kpa kiba la ïa-ai ha kata ka kam. U Tirshatha u la ai ha ka jingkynshew, shi hajar darik ka ksiar, sanphew ki khuri, sanspah laiphew ki jaiñkup lyngdoh.",
			"71": "<sup>71</sup> Bad don kiba na ki rangbah ki ïing ki kpa kiba la ai ha ka jingkynshew kata ka kam, arphew hajar darik ka ksiar, bad ar hajar arspah maneh ka rupa.",
			"72": "<sup>72</sup> Bad kata kaba la ai da kita kiwei pat na u paidbah, ka la long arphew hajar darik ka ksiar, bad ar hajar maneh ka rupa, bad hynñiewphew hynñiew ki jaiñkup lyngdoh.",
			"73": "<sup>73</sup> Kumta ki lyngdoh, bad ki Lebi, bad ki nongap jingkhang, bad ki nongrwai, bad kiba na u paidbah, bad ki Nethin, bad Israel baroh, ki la shong duh ha la ki shnong. Bad haba u 'nai hynñiew u la poi, ki khun Israel ki la don ha la ki shnong."
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad u paidbah baroh, u la ïalum lang ryntih ha ka madan kaba la don ha khmat ka khyrdop um; bad ki la ong ha u Esra u nongthoh ban wallam ïa Ka Kitab Ka Hukum u Moses, ïa kaba U Trai u la lah hukum ha ki Israel.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u Esra lyngdoh u la wallam ïa Ka Hukum ha khmat u paidlang, shynrang bad kynthei, bad baroh kat kiba lah ban sngap da kaba shemphang, ha ka sngi nyngkong u 'nai bahynñiew.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad u la pule na kata, ha khmat ka madan kaba la don ha khmat Ka Khyrdop Um naduh dang shai haduh shiteng sngi, ha khmat ki shynrang bad ki kynthei, bad kita kiba lah ban shemphang; bad ki shkor u paidbah baroh ki la shah ha Ka Kitab Ka Hukum.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad u Esra u nongthoh u la ïeng ha ka pulpit dieng, ïa kaba ki la shna khnang ïa kane; bad hajan jong u, u la ïeng u Mattithiah, bad u Shemah, bad u Anaïah, bad u Uriah, bad u Hilkiah, bad u Maaseïah, sha kamon jong u; bad sha kadiang, u Pediah bad u Mishael, bad u Malkhijah, bad u Hashum, bad u Hashbaddanah, bad u Sekharaïah, bad u Meshullam.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad u Esra u la plie ïa Ka Kitab ha khmat u paidbah baroh; (namar u la long kham hajrong ïa u paidbah baroh;) bad haba u la plie, u paidbah baroh u la ïeng joit;",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> bad u Esra u la kyrkhu ïa U Trai U Blei bakhraw. Bad u paidbah baroh u la ong, “Amen, Amen,” da kaba rah ïa la ki kti: bad ki la dem ïa la ki khlieh, bad ki la mane ïa U Trai la ki khmat sha ka khyndew.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> U Jeshua ruh, bad u Bani, bad u Sherebiah, u Jamin, u Akkub, u Shabbethai, u Hodiah, u Maaseïah, u Kelita, u Asariah, u Josabad, u Hanan, u Pelaïah, bad ki Lebi, ki la pynsngewthuh ïa Ka Hukum ha u paidbah: bad u paidbah u la ïeng ha la ka jaka.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad ki la pule shai ha ka kitab ha Ka Hukum U Blei: bad ki la ai ïa ka jingmut, kumta ba ki la sngewthuh ïa ka jingpule.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad u Nehemaïah, uba la long u Tirshatha, bad u Esra lyngdoh u nongthoh, bad ki Lebi kiba hikai ïa u paidbah, ki la ong ha u paidbah baroh, “Kane ka sngi ka long ka bakyntang ïa U Trai U Blei jong phi; wat sngewsih, lymne ïam.” Namar u paidbah baroh u la ïam, haba ki la ïohsngew ïa ki ktien Ka Hukum.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ynda kumta, u la ong ha ki, “Khie leit, to bam ïa kaba khleiñ, bad dih ïa kaba thiang, bad phah ïa ki bynta ha uta ha uba ym shym la khreh ei ei: namar kane ka sngi, ka long ka bakyntang ha U Trai jong ngi: lymne wat sngewsih; namar ka jingkmen U Trai ka long ka bor jong phi.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Kumta ki Lebi ki la pynjar jar ïa u paidbah baroh, ki ïa-ong, “Sngap jar, namar kane ka sngi, ka long ka bakyntang; bad wat sngewsih.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad u paidbah baroh u la leit noh ban bam, bad ban dih, bad ban phah ki bynta, bad ban leh kmen eh, namar ba ki la lah sngewthuh ïa kita ki ktien kiba la pynbna ha ki.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad ha ka sngi ka ba-ar, ki la ïalum lang ki rangbah ki ïing ki kpa u paidbah baroh, ki lyngdoh, bad ki Lebi, ha u Esra u nongthoh, ban ïoh hikai keiñ ha ki ktien Ka Hukum.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad ki la shem ba la thoh ha Ka Hukum, kumno ba U Trai u la lah hukum da u Moses, ba ka dei ïa ki khun Israel ban shong ha ki ïingtrep, ha Ka Jingkhawai u bnai u bahynñiew:",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> bad ba ka dei ïa ki, ban pynbna bad ban pyntip ha ki shnong jong ki baroh, bad ha Jerusalem, da kaba ong, “Khie leit sha u lum bad wallam ki tnat dieng Olib, bad ki tnat dieng Olib khlaw, bad ki tnat dieng Myrtl, bad ki tnat dieng Tlai, bad ki tnat dieng khah sla, ban shna ki ïingtrep kumba la thoh.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Kumta, u paidbah u la mih noh, bad u la wallam ïa ki, bad ki la shna ki ïingtrep ïa lade, uwei pa uwei halor ka paki ka ïing jong u, bad ha ki phyllaw jong ki, bad ha ki phyllaw ka ïing U Blei, bad ha ka madan ka khyrdop um, bad ha ka madan ka khyrdop Ephraim.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad u paidlang jong kita baroh kiba la wan phai pat na ka jingpynwir ki la shna ïa ki ïingtrep, bad ki la shong ha ki ïingtrep: namar naduh ki sngi u Jeshua u khun u Nun haduh kata ka sngi, ki khun Israel kim shym la leh kumta. Bad la don ka jingkmen bakhraw eh.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Man la ka sngi ruh, naduh ka sngi nyngkong haduh ka sngi khatduh, u la pule ha Ka Kitab Ka Hukum U Blei. Bad ki la rakhe ïa Ka Jingkhawai, hynñiew sngi; bad ha ka baphra sngi, ka la long ka jingïaseng bakhuid, katba kum ka rukom."
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad ha ka ba-arphew saw sngi na une u bnai, ki khun Israel ki la ïalang da kaba shah jingit, bad kup jaiñ byrni, bad ki da ïasleh khyndew de.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u symbai Israel u la pynïakhlad ïa lade na ki nongwei baroh, bad u la ïeng bad u la phla ïa la ki pop, bad ïa ki jingleh bymhok ki kpa jong ki.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad ki la ïaïeng joit ha la ka jaka, bad ki la ïapule ha Ka Kitab Ka Hukum U Trai U Blei jong ki, shi pawa sngi; bad shi pawa pat, ki la ïaphla bad ïamane ïa U Trai U Blei jong ki.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ynda kumta, ki la kiew halor ki kyrdon kiba na ki Lebi, u Jeshua, bad u Bani, u Kadmiel, u Shebaniah, u Bunni, u Sherebiah, u Bani bad u Khenani, bad ki la pyrta da ka ktien bajam ha U Trai U Blei jong ki.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te ki Lebi, u Jeshua, u Kadmiel, u Bani, u Hashabneïah, bad u Sherebiah, u Hodiah, u Shebaniah, bad u Pethahiah, ki la ong, “To ïeng joit bad kyrkhu ïa U Trai U Blei jong phi na ka bymjukut sha ka bymjukut: bad long ba la kyrkhu ïa ka kyrteng ba-donburom jong me, ïa kaba la kyntiew halor ka jingkyrkhu bad ka jingïaroh baroh.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> “Me long U Trai, tang ma me hi; me la thaw ïa ka bneng, ka bneng jong ki bneng, bad ki paidbah jong ki baroh, ïa ka khyndew bad kiei kiei baroh katba don ha ka, ïa ki duriaw bad baroh katba don ha ki, bad me kyrshan ïa ki baroh; bad u paidbah bneng u mane ïa me.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Me long U Trai U Blei, uba la jied ïa u Abram, bad me la wallam noh ïa u na ka Ur ki Khaldi, bad me la kyrteng ïa u, ‘u Abraham’:",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> bad me la shem ïa ka dohnud jong u kaba ïaineh ha khmat jong me, bad me la thaw jutang bad u, ban ai ka ri ki Kanaan, ki Hit, ki Amor, ki Peris, ki Jebus, ki Girgash, ban ai keiñ ha u symbai jong u, bad me la pyndep ïa la ki ktien; namar me long u bahok.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> “Bad me la ïohi ïa ka jingshitom ki kpa jong ngi ha Ijipt, bad me la ïohsngew ïa ka jinglynñiar jong ki harud ka Duriaw Basaw;",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> bad me la pyni ïa ki dak phylla bad ki jingphylla halor u Pharaoh, bad halor ki shakri jong u baroh, bad halor ki briew ka ri jong u baroh; namar me la tip ba ki la leh khraw halor ïa ki; bad me la ïoh nam ïa lade, kumba ha kane ka sngi.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad me la pynkad ïa ka duriaw ha khmat jong ki, ba kumta ki la ïaid lyngba ka duriaw ha ka 'dewrkhiang; bad ïa ki nongbeh jong ki, me la shat ha ki jingjylliew, kum ïa u maw ha ki um bah.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Nalor kane me la ïalam ïa ki ha u rishot lyoh mynsngi; bad ha u rishot ding mynmiet, ban ai jingshai ha ka lynti kaba ki dei ban ïaid.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Me la hiar halor u lum Sinai ruh, bad me la kren bad ki na bneng, bad me la ai ha ki, ïa ki jingbishar bahok bad ki rukom bashisha, ki aiñ bad ki hukum babha:",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> bad me la pyntip ha ki, ïa ka Sabbaton bakhuid jong me, bad me la hukum ïa ki hukum ïa ki, bad ki aiñ, bad ka rukom, da ka kti u Moses u shakri jong me:",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> bad me la ai ïa u kpu na bneng ïa ka jingthngan jong ki, bad me la pynmih ruh ïa ka um ha ki, na u mawsiang ïa ka jingsliang jong ki, bad me la hukum ïa ki, ban leit shapoh ban ïoh ïa ka ri ïa kaba me la rah la ka kti ban ai ïa ki.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> “Hynrei, ma ki bad ki kpa jong ngi ki la leh meng, bad ki la pyneh ïa la ka ryndang, bad kim shym la sngap ïa ki hukum jong me,",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> bad ki la kyrngah ban kohnguh, bad kim shym la kynmaw ïa ki jingphylla kiba me la leh hapdeng jong ki; hynrei, ki la pyneh ïa la ka ryndang, bad ha ka jingïaleh pyrshah jong ki, ki la thung nongïalam ban phai pat sha ka jinglongmraw: hynrei, me long U Blei uba kloi ban map, uba aiei bad uba dap ka jingisynei, uba tud ban bitar, uba kynrei ha ka jingisynei, bad mem shym la kyntait noh ïa ki.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Shisha keiñ, haba ki la thaw ha ki, ïa u khun masi ba la saiñ, bad ki la ong, ‘Une u long U Blei jong me uba la wallam noh ïa me na Ijipt,’ bad ki la pynlong ïa ka jingpankwah bakhraw;",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> pynban, me ha ki jingisynei babun jaid jong me, mem shym la iehnoh noh ïa ki ha ka ri khlaw: u rishot lyoh um shym la kynriah noh na shaneng jong ki mynsngi, ban ïalam ïa ki ha ka lynti; lymne u rishot ding mynmiet, ban pynshai ïa ki, bad ïa ka lynti kaba ki dei ban ïaid.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Me la ai ruh ïa U Mynsiem babha jong me ban hikai ïa ki, bad mem shym la khang noh ïa la ka manna na ki shyntur jong ki, bad me la ai um ha ki, ïa ka jingsliang jong ki.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Jin sawphew snem keiñ, me la bsa ïa ki ha ri khlaw, bad kim shym la kyrduh ei ei; ki jaiñ jong ki kim shym la man rim, bad ki kjat jong ki kim shym la at.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Nalor kane me la ai ki hima bad ki kynja bynriew ha ki, ïa kiba me la sam katba kum ki bynta jong ki: kumta, ki la ïoh ïa ka ri u Sihon, ka ri u syiem ka Heshbon keiñ, bad ka ri u Og u syiem ka Bashan.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ïa ki khun jong ki ruh me la pynroi kum ki khlur bneng, bad me la ïalam ha kata ka ri, shaphang kaba me la ong ha ki kpa jong ki, ba kin ïoh poi ha ka ban ïoh ïa ka.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Kumta, ki khun jong ki, ki la leit shapoh bad ki la ïoh ïa kata ka ri, bad me la pynjop ïa ki trai-shnong kata ka ri, ki Kanaan, ha khmat jong ki, bad me la ai ïa ki ha ka kti jong ki, bad ki syiem jong ki, bad ki kynja bynriew kata ka ri, ba kin leh bad ki katba ki mon.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad ki la jop ïa ki shnong ba la ker kut, bad ïa ka ri kaba sei soh, bad ki la ïoh ïa ki ïing ba la dap da kiei kiei ki babha, ïa ki pukri ba la tih, ïa ki brisoh Waiñ, ïa ki brisoh Olib, bad ki dieng soh kyrhai: kumta, ki la bam bad ki la kdang, bad ki la man sngaid, bad ki la pynsngewbha ïa lade ha ka jingbha bakhraw jong me.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> “Pynban, ki la long ki bymkohnguh bad ki la ïaleh pyrshah ïa me, bad ki la bred noh ïa ki hukum jong me shadien ka ingdong jong ki, bad ki la pynïap ïa ki nongïathuhlypa jong me kiba la phla pyrshah ïa ki, ban pynphai pat ïa ki sha me, bad ki la pynlong ïa ka jingpankwah bakhraw.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Namar kata, me la ai noh ïa ki ha ka kti ki nongshun jong ki, kiba la pynjynjar ïa ki: bad ha ka por ka jingshipa jong ki, haba ki la lynñiar ha me, me la ïohsngew ïa ki na bneng; bad katba kum ki jingisynei ba bun jaid jong me, me la ai ki nongpynim ïa ki kiba la pynim ïa ki na ki kti ki nongshun jong ki.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Hynrei, ynda ki la shongthait, ki la leh sniew pat ha khmat jong me: namar kata, me la iehnoh ïa ki ha ki kti ki nongshun jong ki, kumta, ki la synshar halor jong ki: pynban, haba ki la phai pat, bad ki la lynñiar ha me, me la ïohsngew ïa ki na bneng; bad bunsien me la pyllait ïa ki katba kum ki jingisynei jong me;",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> bad me la phla pyrshah ïa ki, ba me lah ban pynwan pat ïa ki ha ki hukum jong me: pynban, ki la leh meng, bad kim shym la sngap ïa ki hukum jong me, hynrei, ki la leh pop pyrshah ïa ki jingbishar jong me, (kiba lada u briew un leh, un ïoh im ha ki,) bad ki la kynran ïa la ka tyrpeng, bad ki la pyneh ïa la ka ryndang, bad kim shym la sngap.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Pynban, bun snem me la shah ïa ki, bad me la phla pyrshah ïa ki da U Mynsiem jong me da ki nongïathuhlypa: pynban, kim shahshkor; namar kata, me la ai noh ïa ki ha ka kti ki kynja bynriew jong kita ki ri.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Pynban, ha ki jingisynei ba bun jaid jong me, mem shym la pynduh khoit ïa ki, lymne mem shym la kyntait noh ïa ki; namar me long U Blei uba sbun bad uba isynei.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> “Mynta, namar kata, U Blei jong ngi, uba khraw, uba don bor, bad uba itieng, uba sumar ïa ka jutang bad ïa ka jingisynei, wat ai ba kane ka jingshitom baroh kan i rit ha khmat jong me, kaba la jia ïa ngi, ïa ki syiem jong ngi, ïa ki rangbah jong ngi, bad ïa ki lyngdoh jong ngi, bad ïa ki nongïathuhlypa jong ngi, bad ïa ki kpa jong ngi, bad u paidbah jong me baroh, naduh ki sngi ki syiem ka Assyria haduh kane ka sngi.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> La kumta ruh, me long u bahok ha kiei kiei baroh kiba la jia ïa ngi; namar me la leh ïa kaba shisha, hynrei, ngi la leh bymman.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Ki syiem jong ngi ruh, ki rangbah jong ngi, ki lyngdoh jong ngi, bad ki kpa jong ngi, kim shym la rakhe ïa ka hukum jong me, lymne sngap ïa ki hukum bad ki jingphla jong me, da kiba me la phla pyrshah ïa ki.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Namar kim shym la shakri ïa me ha la ka hima, bad ha ka jingbha bakhraw jong me kaba me la ai ha ki, bad ha ka ri ka bakhraw bad basei soh ïa kaba me la buh ha khmat jong ki, lymne kim shym la phai noh na ki jingleh bymman jong ki.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Ha khmih, ngi long ki shakri mynta, bad shaphang kane ka ri ïa kaba me la ai ha ki kpa jong ngi ban bam na u soh jong ka bad na ka jingbha jong ka, ha khmih, ngi long ki shakri ha ka.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Bad ka sei soh shibun ha ki syiem kiba me la buh halor jong ngi namar ki pop jong ngi: ki don bor ruh halor ki met jong ngi, bad halor ki jingri jong ngi, katba ki mon, bad ngi long ha ka jingshipa bakhraw.”",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> La kumta ruh, pynban, ngi thaw jutang baskhem, bad ngi thoh ïa ka; bad ki rangbah jong ngi, ki Lebi jong ngi, bad ki lyngdoh jong ngi, ki ïashon shab ha ka."
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te kita kiba la shon shab ki la long, u Nehemaïah u Tirshatha, u khun u Hakaliah, bad u Sedekaïah;",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> u Seraïah, u Asaraïah, u Jeremaïah;",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> u Pashur, u Amariah, u Malkhijah;",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> u Hattush, u Shebaniah, u Mallukh;",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> u Harim, u Meremoth, u Obadaïah;",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> u Daniel, u Ginnethon, u Barukh;",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> u Meshullam, u Abijah, u Mijamin;",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> u Maasiah, u Bilgai, u Shemaïah: kine ki la long lyngdoh.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad ki Lebi: u Jeshua u khun u Asaniah, u Binnui na ki khun u Henadad, u Kadmiel;",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> bad ki para jong ki, u Shebaniah, u Hodijah, u Kelita, u Pelaïah, u Hanan;",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> u Mikha, u Rehob, u Hashabiah;",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> u Sakkur, u Sherebiah, u Shebaniah;",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> u Hodijah, u Bani, u Beninu.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ki rangbah u paidbah: u Parosh, u Pahath-moab, u Elam, u Satthu, u Bani;",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> u Bunni, u Asgad, u Bebai;",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> u Adonijah, u Bigbai, u Adin;",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> u Ater, u Hesekaïah, u Assur;",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> u Hodijah, u Hashum, u Besai;",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> u Hariph, u Anathoth, u Nebai;",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> u Magpiash, u Meshullam, u Hesir;",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> u Meshesabel, u Sadok, u Jaddua;",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> u Pelatiah, u Hanan, u Anaïah;",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> u Hoshea, u Hananiah, u Hasshub;",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> u Hallohesh, u Pilha, u Shobek;",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> u Rehum, u Hashabnah, u Maaseïah;",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> bad u Ahijah, u Hanan, u Anan;",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> u Mallukh, u Harim, u Baanah.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Bad kita kiwei pat na u paidbah, ki lyngdoh, ki Lebi, ki nongap jingkhang, ki nongrwai, ki Nethin, bad kita baroh kiba la pynkyrpang ïa lade na ki kynja bynriew jong kita ki ri ha Ka Hukum U Blei, ki tnga jong ki, ki khun shynrang jong ki, bad ki khun kynthei jong ki, uwei pa uwei uba don ka jingtip bad ka jingshemphang;",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> ki la ïasnoh bad la ki para, la ki bakhraw batri, bad ki la rung ha ka jingïatang, bad ha ka jingsmai, ban ïaid ha Ka Hukum U Blei, ïa kaba u la ai ha u Moses u shakri U Blei, bad ban rakhe bad ban leh baroh ïa ki hukum U Trai, U Trai jong ngi, bad ki jingbishar jong u bad ki aiñ jong u;",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> bad ba ngin ym ai ïa la ki khun kynthei ha ki kynja bynriew jong kane ka ri, lymne shim ïa ki khun kynthei jong ki ha ki khun shynrang jong ngi:",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> bad lada ki kynja bynriew jong kane ka ri kin wallam ïa ki jingbuh jingsat lane ki kynja jingbam ha ka sngi Sabbaton ban die, ba ngin ym thied na ki ha ka Sabbaton, lymne ha ka sngi bakyntang: bad ba ngin iehnoh noh ïa ka snem ka bahynñiew, bad ïa kaba pan la ka ram baroh.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Bad ngi la buh rukom ruh ha lade, ba ngin siew na lade man la ka snem ïa ka balai bynta bynta shekel ïa ka kam ka ïing U Blei jong ngi;",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> ïa u 'pu pyni, bad ïa ka jingainguh bam kaba ha la ka sngi, bad ïa ka jingainguh thang kaba ha la ka sngi, ki jong ki Sabbaton, ki jong ki 'nai thymmai, ïa Ki Jingkhawai Niam ba la buh, bad ïa kiei kiei ki bakyntang, bad ïa ki jingainguh sait pop ban pynlong jingpynïasuk na ka bynta ki Israel, bad ïa ka kam baroh ka ïing U Blei jong ngi.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Bad ngi la pynnoh ïa ki jingkhalai, ki lyngdoh, ki Lebi, bad u paidbah, shaphang u dieng ka jingainguh, ban wallam ïa u ha ka ïing U Blei jong ngi, katba kum ki ïing ki kpa jong ngi, ha ki por ba la buh, man la ka snem, ban thang ïa ki halor ka duwan U Trai U Blei jong ngi, kumba la thoh ha Ka Hukum:",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> bad ban wallam ïa ki soh nyngkong ka khyndew jong ngi, bad ïa ki soh nyngkong ki kynja dieng soh baroh, man la ka snem, ha ka ïing U Trai:",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> bad kiba kha nyngkong na ki khun shynrang jong ngi ruh, bad na ki jingri jong ngi, kumba la thoh ha Ka Hukum, bad ïa kiba kha nyngkong na ki kynhun masi jong ngi bad na ki kynhun langbrot jong ngi, ban wallam ha ka ïing U Blei jong ngi, ha ki lyngdoh kiba shakri ha ka ïing U Blei jong ngi:",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> bad ba ngin wallam noh na ki soh nyngkong u 'pu im jong ngi, bad ïa ka jingainguh kyntiew, bad ïa u soh ki kynja dieng baroh, ka Waiñ bad ka umphniang, ha ki lyngdoh, ha ki kamra ka ïing U Blei jong ngi; bad ïa kaba shiphew na ka khyndew jong ngi ha ki Lebi; namar ki, ki Lebi, ki shim ïa kaba shiphew ha ki shnong bri jong ngi baroh.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Bad u lyngdoh u khun u Aaron un long lem bad ki Lebi, haba ki Lebi ki shim ïa kaba shiphew: bad ki Lebi kin wallam ïa kaba shiphew na kiba shiphew ha ka ïing U Blei jong ngi, ha ki kamra, ha ka ïing jingkynshew.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Namar ki khun Israel bad ki khun u Lebi kin wallam ïa ka jingainguh kyntiew na u Kew, na ka Waiñ, bad na ka umphniang, ha ki kamra, ha kiba ki don ki khiew ki pliang ka jaka kyntang, bad ki lyngdoh kiba shakri, bad ki nongap jingkhang, bad ki nongrwai: te ngin ym iehnoh ïa ka ïing U Blei jong ngi."
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad ki rangbah u paidbah ki la shong sah ha Jerusalem: kiwei pat de na u paidbah ki la pynnoh ïa ki jingkhalai, ban wallam ïa uwei na shiphew ban shong duh ha Jerusalem ka nongbah bakhuid, bad ki khyndai bynta ha kiwei pat ki shnong.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u paidbah u la kyrkhu ïa kita ki briew baroh kiba la tyrwa sngewbha ïa lade ban shong duh ha Jerusalem:",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Kine te ki long ki rangbah ka shnat kiba la shong duh ha Jerusalem: hynrei, ha ki shnong Judah uwei uwei u la shong ha la ka bynta trai ha ki shnong jong ki, kita ki long, ki Israel, ki lyngdoh, bad ki Lebi, bad ki Nethin, bad ki khun ki shakri u Solomon.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad ha Jerusalem ki la shong kiba na ki khun u Judah bad na ki khun u Benjamin. Na ki khun u Judah: u Athaïah u khun u Ussiah, u khun u Sekharaïah, u khun u Amaraïah, u khun u Shephatiah, u khun u Mahalalil, u khun u Peres;",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> bad u Maaseïah u khun u Barukh, u khun u Kol-hoseh, u khun u Hasaïah, u khun u Adaïah, u khun u Joïarib, u khun u Sekharaïah, u khun u nong Shilon.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Baroh ki khun u Peres kiba shong ha Jerusalem, ki la long sawspah hynriewphew phra, ki briew kiba shlur.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad kine ki long ki khun u Benjamin: u Sallu u khun u Meshullam, u khun u Joed, u khun u Pedaïah, u khun u Kolaïah, u khun u Maaseïah, u khun u Ithiel, u khun u Jeshaïah.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad uba bud ïa u Gabbai, u Sallai, khyndaispah arphew phra.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad u Joel u khun u Sikhri, u la long u sordar jong ki: bad u Judah u khun u Hassenuah u la long u ba-ar halor kata ka nongbah.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na ki lyngdoh: u Jedaïah u khun u Joïarib, u Jakhin,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> u Seraïah u khun u Hilkiah, u khun u Meshullam, u khun u Sadok, u khun u Meraïoth, u khun u Ahitub, u nongsynshar ka ïing U Blei,",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> bad ki para jong ki kiba la trei ïa ka kam kata ka ïing, phraspah arphew ar ngut; bad u Adaïah u khun u Jeroham, u khun u Pelaliah, u khun u Amsi, u khun u Sekharaïah, u khun u Pashur, u khun u Malkhijah,",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> bad ki para jong u, ki rangbah ki ïing ki kpa, arspah sawphew ar: bad u Amashai u khun u Asarel, u khun u Ahsai, u khun u Meshillemoth, u khun u Immer,",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> bad ki para jong ki, ki briew kiba shlur eh, shispah arphew phra: bad u sordar jong ki u la long u Sabdiel, u khun u Haggedolim.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad na ki Lebi: u Shemaïah u khun u Hasshub, u khun u Asrikam, u khun u Hashabiah, u khun u Bunni;",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> bad u Shabbethai bad u Josabad, na ki rangbah ki Lebi, kiba khmih shaphang ka kam kaba shabar ka ïing U Blei;",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> bad u Mattaniah u khun u Mika, u khun u Sabdi, u khun u Asaph, u la long u rangbah ban sdang ïa ka jingainguh ha ka jingduwai, bad u Bakbukiah, u long u ba-ar hapdeng ki para jong u; bad u Abda u khun u Shammua, u khun u Galal, u khun u Jeduthun.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ki Lebi baroh kiba don ha kane ka nongbah bakhuid ki la long arspah phraphew saw ngut.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Nalor kata, ki nongap jingkhang, u Akkub, u Talmon, bad ki para jong ki, kiba la ap ïa ki khyrdop, shispah hynñiewphew ar ngut.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad kiwei pat na ki Israel, na ki lyngdoh, bad na ki Lebi, ki la don ha ki shnong Judah baroh, uwei uwei ha la ka jingïoh pateng.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Hynrei, ki Nethin ki la shong ha Ophel: bad u Siha bad u Gishpa ki la long halor ki Nethin.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> U sordar ki Lebi ruh kiba don ha Jerusalem u la long u Ussi u khun u Bani, u khun u Hashabiah, u khun u Mattaniah, u khun u Mika, na ki khun u Asaph, ki nongrwai, kiba halor ka kam ka ïing U Blei.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Namar la don ka hukum na u syiem shaphang jong ki, bad ka bynta ba la buh ïa ki nongrwai, katba donkam man la ka sngi.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad u Pethahiah u khun u Meshesabel, na ki khun u Serah u khun u Judah, u la don hajan ka kti u syiem ha kiei kiei baroh kiba dei shaphang u paidbah.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad ïa ki nongrit, lem bad ki lyngkha jong ki, don kiba na ki khun u Judah kiba la shong ha Kiriath-arba bad ki shnong jong ka, bad ha Dibon bad ki shnong jong ka, bad ha Jekabsil bad ki shnong jong ka;",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> bad ha Jeshua, bad ha Moladah, bad ha Beth-pelet;",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> bad ha Hasar-shual, bad ha Beer-sheba bad ki shnong jong ka;",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> bad ha Siklag, bad ha Mekonah bad ha ki shnong jong ka;",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> bad ha ka En-rimmon, bad ha Sorah bad ha Jarmuth;",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Sanoah, Adullam, bad ha ki shnong jong ki, ha Lakhish bad ki lyngkha jong ka, Asekah bad ki shnong jong ka. Kumta, ki la shong dara na Beer-sheba haduh ka them Hinnom.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Ki khun u Benjamin ruh, ki la shong na Geba ter ter, haduh Mikhmash bad Aija, bad ha Bethel bad ki shnong jong ka;",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> ha Anathoth, Nob, Ananiah;",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Hasor, Ramah, Gittaim;",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Hadid, Seboim, Neballat;",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Lod, bad Ono, ha them ki nongthaw jingthaw.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Bad na ki Lebi, don ki jingkylliang sngi ha Judah kiba la pynïasoh ha Benjamin."
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te kine ki long ki lyngdoh bad ki Lebi kiba la leit kiew bad u Serubbabel u khun u Shealtiel, bad u Jeshua: u Seraïah, u Jeremaïah, u Esra;",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> u Amariah, u Mallukh, u Hattush;",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> u Shekhanaïah, u Rehum, u Meremoth;",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> u Iddo, u Ginnethoi, u Abijah;",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> u Mijamin, u Maadiah, u Bilgah;",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> u Shemiah, bad u Joïarib, u Jedaïah;",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> u Sallu, u Amok, u Hilkiah, u Jedaïah. Kine ki la long ki rangbah jong ki lyngdoh bad ki para jong ki ha ki sngi u Jeshua.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ba ki Lebi ruh: u Jeshua, u Binnui, u Kadmiel, u Sherebiah, u Judah, bad u Mattaniah, uba la long halor ka jingïaroh, ma u bad ki para jong u.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> U Bakbukiah bad u Unni ruh, ki para jong ki, ki la long marpyrshah ïa ki ha ki jingap.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad u Jeshua u la pynkha ïa u Joïakim, bad u Joïakim u la pynkha ïa u Eliashib, bad u Eliashib u la pynkha ïa u Joïada,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> bad u Joïada u la pynkha ïa u Jonathan, bad u Jonathan u la pynkha ïa u Jaddua.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te ha ki sngi u Joïakim, kine ki la long ki lyngdoh, ki rangbah ki ïing ki kpa; na u Seraïah, u Meraïah; na u Jeremaïah, u Hananiah;",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> na u Esra, u Meshullam; na u Amariah, u Jehohanan;",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> na u Mallukhi, u Jonathan; na u Shebaniah, u Joseph;",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> na u Harim, u Adna; na u Meraïoth, u Helkai;",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> na u Iddo, u Sekharaïah; na u Ginnethon, u Meshullam;",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> na u Abijah, u Sikhri; na u Miniamin, na u Moadiah, u Piltai;",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> na u Bilgah, u Shammua; na u Shemaïah, u Jehonathan;",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> bad na u Joïarib, u Mattenai; na u Jedaïah, u Ussi;",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> na u Sallai, u Kallai; na u Amok, u Eber;",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> na u Hilkiah, u Hashabiah; na u Jedaïah, u Nethanel.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ki Lebi ha ki sngi u Eliashib, u Joïada, bad u Johanan, bad u Jaddua, la thoh ïa ki kum ki rangbah ki ïing ki kpa; ki lyngdoh ruh, haduh ka jingsynshar u Daraïos u nong Persha.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ïa ki khun u Lebi, ki rangbah ki ïing ki kpa, la thoh ha Ka Kitab Ki Khronikl, wat haduh ki sngi u Johanan u khun u Eliashib.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad ki rangbah ki Lebi: u Hashabiah, u Sherebiah, bad u Jeshua u khun u Kadmiel, lem bad ki para jong ki, marpyrshah ïa ki, ban ïaroh bad ban ainguh, katba kum ka hukum u Dabid u briew jong U Blei, mar marpyrshah.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> U Mattaniah, bad u Bakbukiah, u Obadaïah, u Meshullam, u Talmon, u Akkub, ki la long ki nongap kiba ap ha ki ïing kynshew jong ki khyrdop.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Kine ki la long ha ki sngi u Joïakim u khun u Jeshua, u khun u Josadak, bad ha ki sngi u Nehemaïah u nongsynshar, bad u Esra lyngdoh uba u nongthoh.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Bad ha ka jingpynkyntang ïa ka kynroh Jerusalem, ki la wad ïa ki Lebi na ki jaka jong ki baroh, ban wallam ïa ki sha Jerusalem, ban rakhe ïa ka jingpynkyntang da kaba leh kmen, da ki jingainguh, bad ka jingrwai, bad ki ksing, bad ki nebel, bad ki duitara.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Bad ki khun ki nongrwai ki la ïalum lang ïa lade, na ka madan baroh sawdong ka Jerusalem, bad na ki nongrit ki Netophath;",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> na Beth-gilgal ruh, bad na ki lyngkha Geba bad Asmabeth: namar ki nongrwai ki la lah thaw shnong ïa lade baroh sawdong ka Jerusalem.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Bad ki lyngdoh bad ki Lebi ki la pynkhuid ïa lade; ki la pynkhuid ïa u paidbah ruh, bad ïa ki khyrdop, bad ïa ka kynroh.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Te nga la wallam noh ïa ki rangbah Judah halor ka kynroh, bad nga la buh ar kynhun bakhraw kiba la ïaroh bad ïaid ryntih, na kita kawei ka la ïaid na shaphang kamon ha ka kynroh shaphang Ka Khyrdop Synrum:",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> bad hadien jong ki, u la leit u Hoshaïah, bad marshiteng na ki rangbah Judah,",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> bad u Asariah, u Esra, bad u Meshullam,",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> u Judah, bad u Benjamin, bad u Shemaïah, bad u Jeremaïah,",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> bad kiba na ki khun ki lyngdoh kiba bad ki ronsing: u Sekharaïah, u khun u Jonathan, u khun u Shemaïah, u khun u Mattaniah, u khun u Mikhaïah, u khun u Sakkur, u khun u Asaph;",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> bad ki para jong u, u Shemaïah, bad u Asarel, u Milalai, u Gilalai, u Maai, u Nethanel, bad u Judah, u Hanani, bad ki jingtem jong u Dabid u briew jong U Blei: bad u Esra u nongthoh ha shuwa jong ki:",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> bad hajan Ka Khyrdop Umpohliew, bad beit sha shuwa jong ki, ki la kiew noh na ki kyrdon ka shnong u Dabid, ha kaba kiew ka kynroh, shaneng ka ïing u Dabid, wat haduh Ka Khyrdop Um shaphang mihngi.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Bad kata kawei pat ka kynhun na kita kiba la ïaroh ka la leit ban ïashem bad ki, bad ma nga hadien jong ki, lem bad marshiteng na u paidbah, halor ka kynroh, shaneng ka ïingphira ki pajwa, wat haduh ka kynroh baïar;",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> bad shaneng Ka Khyrdop Ephraim, bad hajan Ka Khyrdop barim, bad na Ka Khyrdop Dohkha, bad ka ïing phira Hananil, bad ka ïing phira Hammeah, wat haduh Ka Khyrdop Langbrot; bad ki la ïeng prem ha Ka Khyrdop Nongap.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Kumta, ki la ïeng kine ki ar ki kynhun kiba la ïaroh ha ka ïing U Blei, bad ma nga, bad shiteng na ki nongsynshar lem bad nga:",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> bad ki lyngdoh, u Eliakim, u Maaseïah, u Miniamin, u Mikaïah, u Elioenai, u Sekharaïah, bad u Hananiah, kiba bad ki ronsing;",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> bad u Maaseïah, bad u Shemaïah bad u Eleasar, bad u Ussi, bad u Jehohanan, bad u Malkhijah, bad u Elam, bad u Eser. Bad ki nongrwai ki la rwai jam, bad u Jesrahiah halor jong ki.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Bad ki la kñia ïa ki jingkñia shibun ha ka kata ka sngi, bad ki la leh kmen; namar U Blei u la pynkmen ïa ki da ka jingkmen bakhraw; bad ki kynthei de bad ki khynnah ki la leh kmen: bad kumta ka jingkmen ka Jerusalem la ïohsngew na sha jngai.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Bad ha kata ka sngi, la buh ïa ki briew halor ki pulit ki jingkynshew, ki jingainguh kyntiew ki soh nyngkong, bad ki khajna, ban ïalum ha ki, na ki lyngkha ki shnong, ïa ki bynta ba la buh da Ka Hukum ïa ki lyngdoh bad ki Lebi: naba ki Judah ki la kmen namar ki lyngdoh bad ki Lebi kiba la ap.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Bad ki la ap ïa ka jingap U Blei jong ki, bad ïa ka jingap ka jingpynkhuid, bad ki nongrwai bad ki nongap jingkhang ki la leh kumjuh, katba kum ka hukum u Dabid, bad u Solomon u khun jong u.",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Namar ha ki sngi u Dabid bad u Asaph, na mynbarim don u rangbah ki nongrwai, bad ki jingrwai ïaroh bad jingainguh ha U Blei.",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> Te ki Israel baroh ha ki sngi u Serubbabel, bad ha ki sngi u Nehemaïah, ki la ai ïa ki bynta jong ki nongrwai bad ki nongap jingkhang, katba donkam man la ka sngi; bad ki la buh kyrpang ïa ki Lebi; bad ki Lebi ki la buh kyrpang ïa ki khun u Aaron."
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ha kata ka sngi, ki la pule ha Ka Kitab u Moses ha kaba ïohsngew u paidbah; bad la shem ba la thoh ha ka, ba ym bit ïa u nong Ammon bad u nong Moab ban rung hapoh ka jingïaseng U Blei lano lano ruh;",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> namar ba kim shym la leit tan ïa ki khun Israel bad u kpu bad ka um, hynrei, ki la wer nong ïa u Balaam ban ïaleh ïa ki, ban tim ïa ki: hynrei, U Blei jong ngi u la pynkylla ïa ka jingtim sha ka jingkyrkhu.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te ka la jia, haba ki la ïohsngew ïa ka hukum, ba ki la pynkhlad na ki Israel ïa u paidbah baïakhleh baroh.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te shuwa ïa kane, u Eliashib lyngdoh, uba la buh halor ki pulit ka ïing U Blei jong ngi, bad u da long uba la ïasoh lok bad u Tobiah,",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> u la lah khreh lypa ïa u ka pulit bakhraw, ha kaba ki la buh mynshuwa ïa ki jingainguh bam, ïa ka jingiwbih, bad ïa ki pliang ki luta, bad ïa kaba shiphew na u Kew, na ka Waiñ, bad na ka umphniang, ïa kiba la ai da ka hukum ha ki Lebi, bad ha ki nongrwai, bad ha ki nongap jingkhang; bad ïa ki jingainguh kyntiew ïa ki lyngdoh.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Hynrei, ha kane ka por baroh ngam shym la don ha Jerusalem: namar ha ka balaiphew ar ka snem u Artakserksis u syiem ka Babilon nga la leit sha u syiem, bad hadien katto katne sngi nga la pan shuti na u syiem:",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> bad nga la poi ha Jerusalem, bad nga la sngewthuh ïa ka jingleh bymman ba u Eliashib u la leh na ka bynta u Tobiah, da kaba u la khreh ïa u ka pulit ha ki phyllaw ka ïing U Blei.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Kane te ka la pynsngewsih sat ïa nga: namar kata, nga la bred noh ïa ki mar ki mata u Tobiah na kata ka pulit.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te nga la ai hukum, bad ki la pynkhuid ïa ki pulit: bad nga la wallam hangta pat ïa ki pliang ki luta ka ïing U Blei, lem bad ka jingainguh bam bad ka jingiwbih.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Nga la tip ruh ba ym shym la ai ïa ki bynta ki Lebi ha ki; ba namar kata ki Lebi bad ki nongrwai, kiba trei ïa ka kam, ki la ïaphet noh baroh sha la ka lyngkha.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te nga la ïaleh ïa ki nongsynshar, bad nga la ong, “Balei ba la kyntait ïa ka ïing U Blei?” Te nga la ïalum lang ïa ki, bad nga la buh ïa ki ha la ka jaka jaka.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te ka Judah baroh ka la wallam ïa kaba shiphew na u Kew bad na ka Waiñ bad na ka umphniang ha ki jaka jingkynshew.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad nga la buh ïa ki nongsumar jingkynshew halor ki jaka jingkynshew, u Shelemiah lyngdoh, bad u Sadok nongthoh, bad na ki Lebi, u Pedaïah: bad uba bud ïa ki, u la long u Hanan, u khun u Sakkur, u khun u Mattaniah: namar ba la ñiew ïa ki kiba ïaineh, bad ka kam jong ki ka la long ban ïasam ha ki para jong ki.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> “Kynmaw ïa nga, A U Blei jong nga, shaphang kane, bad wat pyndam noh ïa ki jingleh babha jong nga kiba nga la leh ïa ka ïing U Blei jong nga, bad ïa ki kam jong ka.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ha kita ki sngi, nga la ïohi ha Judah, kiba ïuh ïa ka kor tylliat Waiñ ha ka sngi Sabbaton, bad kiba da wallam ïa ki thup Kew, bad ki da pynkit ïa ki kadda da kita; ïa ka Waiñ ruh, ki soh Waiñ, bad ki soh Dumbur, bad ki kynja jingkit baroh, ïa kiba ki la wallam ha Jerusalem, ha ka sngi Sabbaton: bad nga la kren pyrshah ïa ki ha kata ka sngi ha kaba ki la die ïa ki kynja jingbam.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ki briew na Tyros ruh ki la shong ha ka, kiba la wallam dohkha, bad kynja jingdie baroh, bad ki la die ha ka sngi Sabbaton ha ki khun Judah, bad Jerusalem.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te nga la ïaleh ïa ki bakhraw batri jong ka Judah, bad nga la ong ha ki, “Kaei ka basniew ba phi leh, bad ba phi leh sang ha ka sngi Sabbaton?",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ki kpa jong phi kim shym la leh kumne, bad U Blei Um shym la pynwan ïa kane ka jingsniew baroh halor jong ngi, bad halor kane ka shnong? Pynban, phi nang wallam ïa ka jingbitar shuh shuh halor ki Israel da kaba leh sang ha ka sngi Sabbaton.”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te haba ki khyrdop Jerusalem ki la sdang dum shuwa ka sngi Sabbaton, nga la hukum ba yn khang noh ïa ki jingkhang, bad nga la hukum ba yn ym plie ïa ki haduh ba ynda lah ka Sabbaton: bad nga la buh na ki shakri jong nga ban ap ïa ki khyrdop, ba yn ym wallam jingkit ei ei hapoh ha ka sngi Sabbaton.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Kumta, ki nongkhaïi bad ki nongdie ki kynja jingdie baroh ki la shong basa shabar Jerusalem shi sien ar sien.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te nga la kren pyrshah ïa ki, bad nga la ong ha ki, “Balei phi shong basa sawdong ka kynroh? Lada phin leh kumne shuh, ngan kem ïa phi.” Naduh kata ka por, kim shym la wan shuh ha ka sngi Sabbaton.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te nga la hukum ïa ki Lebi ba kin pynkhuid ïa lade, ba kin wan ap ïa ki khyrdop, ban sumar kyrpang ïa ka sngi Sabbaton. “Kynmaw ïa nga, A U Blei jong nga, ïa kane ruh, bad ri pynim ïa nga katba kum ka jingkhraw ka jingisynei jong me.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ha kita ki sngi, nga la ïohi ïa kita ki Jiw kiba la shongkurim ïa ki kynthei Ashdod, Ammon, bad Moab:",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> bad ki khun jong ki, ki la kren khleh Ashdod, bad kim lah ban kren Jiw, hynrei, katba kum ka ktien jong kawei kawei ka kynja bynriew.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te nga la ïaleh ïa ki, bad nga la tim ïa ki, bad nga la shoh kiba na ki, bad nga la phut noh ïa u shñiuh jong ki, bad nga la pynsmai ïa ki da U Blei, nga da ong, “Phin ym ai kurim ïa ki khun kynthei jong phi ha ki khun shynrang jong ki, lymne phin ym shim kurim na ki khun kynthei jong ki ha ki khun shynrang jong phi, lymne ha lade hi.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> U Solomon u syiem ki Israel um shym la leh pop da kine kiei kiei? pynban, hapdeng bun ki kynja bynriew ym shym la don u syiem kum ma u, bad la ieit ïa u da U Blei jong u, bad U Blei u la thung syiem ïa u halor ki Israel baroh; pynban, wat ïa u ki kynthei nongwei ki la pynleh pop.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ngin sngap te ïa phi ban leh ïa kane ka jingsniew bakhraw, ïa ka ban ryngkang pyrshah ïa U Blei jong ngi da kaba shongkurim ïa ki kynthei nongwei?”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Te uwei na ki khun u Joïada, u khun u Eliashib u rangbah lyngdoh, u la long u pyrsa kurim u Sanballat u nong Horon; namar kata, nga la beh noh ïa u na nga.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> “Kynmaw ïa ki, A U Blei jong nga, namar ki la pyntngit ïa ka jinglong lyngdoh, bad ïa ka jutang jinglong lyngdoh, bad jong ki Lebi.”",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Kumne nga la pynkhuid ïa ki na ki nongwei baroh, bad nga la buh ïa ki jingap ïa ki lyngdoh bad ïa ki Lebi, uwei uwei baroh ha la ka kam;",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> bad ïa ki dieng ka jingainguh, ha ki por ba la buh, bad ïa ki soh nyngkong. “Kynmaw ïa nga, A U Blei jong nga, ban pynbha.”"
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;